                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                            <locus from="1r" to="3v"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT4750GadlaGK">Gadla Gabra Krǝstos</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <note>The text begins abruptly, the original beginning of the manuscript is lost.</note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez"><gap reason="lost"/>ለውሉድነ፡ <sic>በመዋዕሊና፡</sic> ወነበቦ፡ ወንትፌሣሕ፡
                                በመርዓሁ፡ ወሐጸዩ፡ ሎቱ፡ ወለተ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ሮምያ፡</incipit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                            <locus from="4ra" to="51rb"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2616Zenaes">Zenā ʾƎskǝndǝr</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <note>The text begins abruptly, the original beginning is missing.
                            The text contained on <locus target="#4"/> corresponds to 
                                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/IQFR7EJN"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Budge1896Alexander1"/><title level="m">The Life and Exploits of Alexander the Great: Being a Series of Ethiopic Texts Edited from Manuscripts in the British Museum and the Bibliothèque nationale, Paris, With an English Translation and Notes&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I:&lt;/hi&gt; The Ethiopic Text, Introduction, etc.</title><author><forename>E. A. Wallis</forename><surname>Budge</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>C. J. Clay and Sons</publisher><date>1896</date><biblScope unit="volume">I</biblScope><note type="url">http://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/ssg/content/titleinfo/1081701</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Literature</note><note type="tag">bm:Budge1896Alexander1</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Literature</note><note type="tag">bm:Budge1896Alexander1</note><citedRange unit="chapter">II</citedRange><citedRange unit="page">267, l. 15–269, l. 1</citedRange></bibl>.
                                The text starting on <locus target="#5"/> follows after a lacuna and corresponds to 
                                <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/IQFR7EJN"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Budge1896Alexander1"/><title level="m">The Life and Exploits of Alexander the Great: Being a Series of Ethiopic Texts Edited from Manuscripts in the British Museum and the Bibliothèque nationale, Paris, With an English Translation and Notes&lt;hi rend="italics"&gt;, I:&lt;/hi&gt; The Ethiopic Text, Introduction, etc.</title><author><forename>E. A. Wallis</forename><surname>Budge</surname></author><pubPlace>London</pubPlace><publisher>C. J. Clay and Sons</publisher><date>1896</date><biblScope unit="volume">I</biblScope><note type="url">http://menadoc.bibliothek.uni-halle.de/ssg/content/titleinfo/1081701</note><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Literature</note><note type="tag">bm:Budge1896Alexander1</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Literature</note><note type="tag">bm:Budge1896Alexander1</note><citedRange unit="chapter">III</citedRange><citedRange unit="page">273</citedRange></bibl>
                                (starting with <foreign xml:lang="gez">ወሰማይኒ፡ ተንጣበጥብ፡</foreign>).
                            </note>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ይጥፍአሙ፡ በማየ፡ ባሕረ፡ ኤርትራ፡ ወፈነወ፡ ኀቤሆሙ፡</incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                                <locus from="51ra" to="51rb"/>
                                    ወተጽኀፈ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ ፴፮ ዓመተ፡ ምኅረት፡ ዘአ<cb n="b"/>ጽሐፈ፡ 
                                <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14719Simi"><roleName type="title">አቶ</roleName>ሲም፡</persName> ተአሚኖ፡ በጸሎቱ፡ 
                                <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3874eskender">ለእስክንድር፡</persName> ንጉሥ፡ 
                                ይዕቀብ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ነፍሱ፡ ወሥጋሁ፡ ወብእሲቱ፡ ወውሉዱ፡ ወአግብርቲሁ፡ 
                                ወጥሪቱ፡ ዘቤት፡ ወዘገዳም፡ 
                                በእደ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ወበገብርኤል፡ <sic>ዜነዌ፡</sic> ትፍስኅት።
                                ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። — ለዘፀሐፎ፡ ወለ<supplied reason="omitted">ዘ</supplied>አጽሐፎ፡ ወለዘ፡ አንበቦ፡ ወዘተርጐሞ፡ ወዘሰምዐ፡ ቃላቲሁ፡ ኅቡረ፡ 
                                ይምሐሮሙ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ <sic>በማንግሥተ፡</sic> ሰማያት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን። — ስረዩ፡ ወባርኩኒ፡ ለገብርክሙ፡ ኀጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡ <sic>ወጊጉዩ፡</sic>
                                ወድኩም፡ ኢትርስዑኒ።
                                </explicit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                            <locus from="51va" to="56ra"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2692Penit">Penitential Canons [not to Peter]</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">በአኰቴተ፡ አብ፡ ወወልደ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ጸሐ<surplus>፡</surplus>ፍነ፡
                                ቀኖን፡ ዘይትነገር፡ ላዕለ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘይትነሳሕ፡ በእንተ፡ ኃጢአቱ፡ ወእመኒ፡ ክርስቲያናዊ፡ ቀተለ፡ ኢያቅልሉ፡ እምንስሓሁ። 
                                ቀኖን፡ እመቦ፡ ሰብእ፡ ዘቀተለ፡ እምአዝማዲሁ፡</incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                                <locus from="55vb" to="56ra"/>
                                ቀኖን፡ ላዕለ፡ ብእሲ፡ ዘይዜሙ፡ ምስለ፡ ብእሲት፡ ተንበለታዊት፡ አው፡ አረማዊት፡ አው፡ ብእሲት፡ ምስለ፡ ብእሲ፡ ታንበለታዊ<surplus>ት</surplus>፡ 
                                አው፡ አረማዊ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/><pb n="56r"/><cb n="a"/> ይቤሉ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ እዙዝ፡ በሲኖዶስ። ለዘጸሐፎ፡ ወለዘ፡ አጽሐፎ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                                እምብዙኅ፡ ብዕለዝ፡ ዐለም፡ ይኄይስ፡ ምርጕዘ፡ ጽድቅ፡ በንስሓ፡ ምስለ፡ ትኅትና፡ ወያውሃት፡ ወትዕግስት፡ ወምስለ፡ 
                                አፍቅሮ፡ ቢጽ፡ ወበዝ፡ ኵሉ፡ ግበሩ፡ ወአጥርዩ፡ ከመ፡ ትረሱ፡ መንግስተ፡ ሰማያት።</explicit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                            <locus from="56r" to="60r"/>
                            <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1941Mashaf">Maṣḥafa lǝdatā la-Māryām</title>
                            <textLang mainLang="gez"/>
                            <incipit xml:lang="gez">ንቅድም፡ በረድኤተ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ኢየሱስ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ንጽሐፍ፡ መጽሐፈ፡ ልደታ፡ ለማርያም፡ <sic>እግዚእተነ፡</sic> ወላዲተ፡ አምላክ፡ ሀሎ፡ 
                                ፩ ብእሲ፡ እምነ፡ ፲ወ፪ ነገደ፡ ደቂቀ፡ እስራኤል፡ ዘስሙ፡ ኢያቄም፡</incipit>
                            <explicit xml:lang="gez">ለዘጸሐፎ፡ ወለዘ፡ አጽሐፎ፡ <gap reason="ellipsis"/></explicit>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
                            <locus from="69ra" to="83ra"/>
                            <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1295Dersan">Dǝrsāna Mikāʾel</title>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i5.1">
                                <locus from="69ra" to="75ra"/>
                                <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1637Homily">Homily on the Archangel Michael by Timothy of Alexandria
     (Ḫǝdār)</title>
                                <note>For <date ref="ethiocal:Hedar12">12 Ḫǝdār</date>.</note>
                                <note>A leaf is missing between <locus target="#72"/> and <locus target="#73"/>.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ድርሳን፡ <supplied reason="omitted">ዘ</supplied>ነገረ፡ ቅዱስ፡ አባ፡ ድማትዮስ፡ ሊቀ፡ ጳጳሳት፡ 
                                    ዘእለስክንድርያ፡ በበዓለ፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ሚካኤል፡ አመ፡ ፲ወ፪፡ ዕለቱ፡ ለኅዳር፡
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i5.2">
                                <locus from="75rb" to="80ra"/>
                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3964Homily">Homily on the Archangel Michael (for Sane)</title>
                                <note>For <date ref="ethiocal:Sane12">12 Sane</date>.</note>
                                <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ድርሳን፡ ወመንክር፡ ዘሚካኤል፡ ሊቀ፡ መላእክት፡ ዘደረሰ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ጳጳስ፡  ዘአክ<sic>።=።=።</sic>ሡም፡ ቀዳሚሆን፡ ለአብያተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ቤተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ 
                                    ወያፈቅርዎ፡ ለ<pb n="75vb"/>ሚካኤል፡ ብዙኃ፡ ፍቅረ፡ በውእቱ፡ ብሔር፡ 
                                    ወሀሎ፡ ፩ መኰንን፡ ዐቢይ፡ ወርቱዕ፡ ሃይማኖቱ፡ ብዙኀ፡ 
                                    ዘስሙ፡ አስታራኒቆስ፡ የቀል፡
                                </incipit>
                            </msItem>
                            
                            <msItem xml:id="ms_i5.3">
                                <locus from="86rb" to="83ra"/>
                                <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT7174MiracleMichaelMoneyFish">Miracle of St Michael on the poor who sent the
     money to the church custodian inside a fish</title>
                                 <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                                    ወኮነ፡ እምድኅረ፡ ዝንቱ፡ <sic>ነገረ፡</sic> ወሀለወ፡ አሐዱ፡ ነዳይ፡ 
                                    <supplied reason="omitted">በ</supplied>ውእቱ፡ ብሔር፡ ወዐቢይ፡ ሃይማኖቱ፡ ወይጼሊ፡ ወይስእል፡ 
                                    መዐልተ፡ <sic>ወሌሊት፡</sic> ወይብል፡ ሚካኤል፡ ሊቅየ፡ ተሣሀለኒ። 
                                    ወሀካይ፡ ወእቱ፡ ብእሲ፡ ኢይወጽእ፡ በውስተ፡ ቤቱ፡ 
                                    <sic>ወአይትገበር፡</sic> ወኢአሐተኒ፡ ዕለተ፡ ወአልቦቱ፡ ስራሕ፡ 
                                    ወእምዝ፡ <add place="below">መ</add>ጽአ፡ ሚካኤል፡ በሕልም፡ ኀበ፡ ዝኩ፡ ነዳይ፡ 
                                    ወይቤሎ፡ እፎ፡ አንተ፡ ሀካይ፡ ብእሲ፡ ኢተአምር፡ 
                                    ስራሕ፡ ወተግባር።
                                </incipit>
                                <colophon xml:id="coloph1" xml:lang="gez">
                                    <locus target="#83ra"/>
                                    ወእለ፡ ሰማዕክሙ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ቃለ፡ ዝንቱ፡ መጽሐፍ፡ በልብ፡ ንጹሕ፡ 
                                    ወዘ፡ አንበበ፡ ወዘቆመ፡ እስከ፡ ይትፈጸም፡ ወዘአጽሐፈ፡ 
                                    <persName role="patron" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14719Simi"><roleName type="title">ለአቶ</roleName>ሲሚ፡</persName> ተአሚኖ፡ በጸሎተ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወለኵልክሙ፡ 
                                    ያውርስክሙ፡ መንግሥተ፡ ሰማያት፡ በጸሎተ፡ ሚካኤል። 
                                    ወበጸ<cb n="b"/>ሎታ፡ ለማርያም፡ ወለዛቲ፡ መካን፡ ኢይባእ፡ ጸራዊ፡ 
                                    ወይዕቀብ፡ ደቂቃ፡ ወአእሩጊሃ፡ እምብድብድ፡ ወእምነኪር፡ 
                                    ሞት፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።
                                    ወለዘ፡ ጸሐፍክዋ፡ አነ፡ <persName role="scribe" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14720Berhan"><roleName type="title">አቶ</roleName>ብርሃን፡</persName> እመሂ፡ ገድለ፡ ሚካኤል፡ ወገድለ፡ ማርያም፡ ወገድለ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ወልደ፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወገድለ፡ እንክንድር፡ ንጉሥ፡ ወመጽሐፈ፡ ቀኖን። 
                                    ኢትርስዑኒ፡ በጸሎትክሙ፡ ለገብርክሙ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ። እመሂ፡ ገደፍኩ፡ ወእመሂ፡ ገንጰልኩ፡ ስረዩ፡ ወባርኩኒ፡ ለገብርክሙ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለመ፡ አሜን። ወአሜን፡ ለይኩን።
                                    <pb n="83v"/><cb n="a"/> ወተፈጸመት፡ ዛቲ፡ መጽሐፍ፡
                                    <date when-custom="36">በ፴ወ፮ ዐመተ፡ ምሕረት፡</date> በመዋዕሊሁ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10626ZaraY">ለዘርአ፡ ያዕቆብ፡</persName> ንጉሥ፡ 
                                    <sic>ወሱዩመ፡</sic> ሐመሴን፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14721Beemnat">ብእምነት፡</persName>
                                    ወመኰንን፡ ዘትግራይ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10623Zaras">ዘርአ፡ ሰናይ።</persName>
                                    <note>
                                        Strelcyn has interpreted the date 36 <foreign xml:lang="gez">ʿāmata mǝḥrat</foreign> as missing the 
                                        indication of the century, thus referring to 
                                        <date calendar="ethiopian" when-custom="1436" notBefore="1443" notAfter="1444">1436</date>, 
                                        which would correspond to 1443/44 CE (<bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/N6HPGQK3"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Strelcyn1976Catalogue"/><title level="m">Catalogue des manuscrits éthiopiens de l’Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei: Fonds Conti Rossini et Fonds Caetani 209, 375, 376, 377, 378</title><title level="s">Indici e Sussidi Bibliografici della Biblioteca</title><author><forename>Stefan</forename><surname>Strelcyn</surname></author><pubPlace>Roma</pubPlace><publisher>Accademia Nazionale dei Lincei</publisher><date>1976</date><series><title level="s">Indici e Sussidi Bibliografici della Biblioteca</title><biblScope unit="volume">9</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">9</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1976Catalogue</note></note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Cataloguing</note><note type="tag">bm:Strelcyn1976Catalogue</note><citedRange unit="page">20</citedRange></bibl>).
                                        Uhlig proposes instead 
                                        that it
                                        refers to the year <date calendar="grace" when-custom="36" notBefore="1459" notAfter="1460">36</date> of the third cycle of the ‘Years of Grace’ that 
                                        began in 1423/24, which would date the manuscript to 1459/60, a time that according to him is 
                                        more consistent with its paleography (<bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MIBCP4VG"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Uhlig1988Palaographie"/><title level="m">Äthiopische Paläographie</title><title level="s">Äthiopistische Forschungen</title><author><forename>Siegbert</forename><surname>Uhlig</surname></author><pubPlace>Stuttgart</pubPlace><publisher>Franz Steiner Verlag GmbH</publisher><date>1988</date><series><title level="s">Äthiopistische Forschungen</title><biblScope unit="volume">22</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">22</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Codicology</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Palaeography</note><note type="tag">bm:Uhlig1988Palaographie</note></note><note type="tag">Codicology</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Palaeography</note><note type="tag">bm:Uhlig1988Palaographie</note><citedRange unit="page">351</citedRange></bibl>).
                                        The identification of the <foreign xml:lang="gez">መኰንን፡ ዘትግራይ፡</foreign> Zarʿa Śannāy,
                                        mentioned in this colophon together with <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10626ZaraY">Zarʾa Yāʿqob</persName>, with the
                                        <foreign xml:lang="gez">Tǝgre makʷannan</foreign> of the same name who was
                                        in office during the reign of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS6229LebnaDe">Lǝbna Dǝngǝl</persName> seems possible, but not certain.</note>
                                </colophon>
                            </msItem>
