                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#83vb"/>
                                    <desc type="CommemorativeNote">Short commemorative note 
                                        by an untrained hand different from the one of <ref target="#a1"/>, mentioning
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14723Giyorgis">Giyorgis</persName>.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">አመ፡ <date ref="ethiocal:Miyazya6">፮ ለሚያዝያ፡</date> ትዘከር፡ አቡነ፡ አዳም፡
                                        አሜሃ፡ አዕረፈ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14723Giyorgis">ጊዮርጊስ፡</persName> ወልደ፡ 
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14724Anbasa">አቶንበሣ።</persName></q>
                                </item>
                                
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus target="#84ra"/>
                                    <desc type="CommemorativeNote">Short commemorative note 
                                        by an untrained hand, mentioning
                                        <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14725Zakkaryas">Zakkāryās</persName>. This person might be identical
                                        to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10539Zakarya"><roleName type="title">qasis ḥaṣ́ay</roleName> 
                                            Zakkāryās</persName> attested at the time of <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS10626ZaraY">Zarʾa Yāʿqob</persName> 
                                        (<bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/MIBCP4VG"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Uhlig1988Palaographie"/><title level="m">Äthiopische Paläographie</title><title level="s">Äthiopistische Forschungen</title><author><forename>Siegbert</forename><surname>Uhlig</surname></author><pubPlace>Stuttgart</pubPlace><publisher>Franz Steiner Verlag GmbH</publisher><date>1988</date><series><title level="s">Äthiopistische Forschungen</title><biblScope unit="volume">22</biblScope></series><biblScope unit="volume">22</biblScope><note type="tags"><note type="tag">Codicology</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Palaeography</note><note type="tag">bm:Uhlig1988Palaographie</note></note><note type="tag">Codicology</note><note type="tag">Ethiopic</note><note type="tag">Palaeography</note><note type="tag">bm:Uhlig1988Palaographie</note><citedRange unit="page">351</citedRange><citedRange unit="note">74</citedRange></bibl>).
                                        According to <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS8999Strelcyn">Stefan Strelcyn</persName>, the date given as
                                    ‘233’ should be corrected in two steps first to ‘1233’ and then to ‘1433’, which would correspond to 1440/41 CE.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">በ<date when-custom="233">፪፴ወ፫ አመተ፡ ምሕረት፡</date> ሞቱ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14725Zakkaryas">ዘካርያስ፡</persName> ቀሲስ። 
                                        እመ፡ ፲ወ፱ <sic>ለሰ<add place="below">ይ</add>ኔ፡</sic> <sic>ተስካሮሙ፡ ።</sic>
                                        ጸሎቱ፡ ትርድአኒ፡ ለለ፡ ሰአቱ፡ ወለለ፡ እለቱ፡ ለወልዱ፡ <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14726TasfaM">ተስፋ<supplied reason="omitted">፡</supplied> ማርያም፡</persName> ዘየሐውር፡ በስምረቱ፡ ወይረሲ፡ ክፍሎ፡ 
                                        ምስለ፡ ሐዋርያት፡ ዘይፈቱ፡ ሀገረ፡ ሰንበት፡ <sic>ይእቱ።</sic></q>
                                </item>
                                
